# {{lb|tr|transitive}} to [[burn]] (CD, DVD)
# {{lb|tr|transitive}} to [[compose]]
# {{lb|tr|transitive}} to [[enroll]], [[register]]; to [[enlist]], [[sign]], [[record]], note down
